data.description: SUNSET LODGE - A COUNTRY LOG HOME IN UPPER MT. BETHEL TOWNSHIP-   The moment you arrive you know you found someplace special.  Meander down the macadam driveway to a masterpiece.  Offering many fine appointments including HWD FLOORS, GRANITE COUNTERS, SS APPLIANCES, CENTRAL AIR, GAS HEAT, LOFT, SUNROOM and much more.   A RARE FIND in great COMMUTER LOCATION.  Over 5,000 sq ft of living space with SUPERIOR CONSTRUCTION!  Offering a FIRST FLOOR PRIMARY BEDROOM SUITE and more bedrooms on the lower level.  UNIQUE and INVITING with room for family and friends.  You will love the GREAT ROOM with FLOOR TO CEILING STONE FPL, MASSIVE KING POST BEAMS,  HWD FLOORS, CATHEDRAL CEILING and FRENCH DOORS leading to a spacious deck.  Capture the DRAMATIC SUNSETS on over 10 ACRES!!  Property is in Act 319 offering low taxes.  Entertain in the rec room and relax by the fire pit outside.  Make memories at SUNSET LODGE!  Close to NJ, NY, and the Lehigh Valley.  Call today!
